---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.tsx";
---

<Layout>
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto pt-8 pb-16 px-4 md:px-8">
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="mb-10 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          {/* Libro de Reclamaciones Icon */}
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-slate-50 border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-4 bg-[#f04f23]"></div>
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-[#0d1624] mt-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-black text-[#0d1624] tracking-tight uppercase mb-2">Libro de Reclamaciones Virtual</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-[14px] leading-relaxed">
            Conforme a lo establecido en el Código de Protección y Defensa del Consumidor, contamos con un Libro de Reclamaciones a tu disposición. Llena el siguiente formulario y te responderemos a la brevedad posible.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 text-[13px]">
            <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md font-semibold">RUC: 20613311808</span>
            <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md font-semibold">Razón Social: GRUPO EMPRESARIAL ZEVALLOS S.A.C.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form id="complaintForm" class="space-y-12">
        {/* Sección 1: Datos del Consumidor */}
        <section>
          <h3 class="flex items-center text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0d1624] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <span class="bg-[#f04f23] text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] mr-3">1</span>
            Identificación del Consumidor Reclamante
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Nombres y Apellidos Completos *</label>
              <input type="text" id="consumerName" name="consumerName" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Tipo de Documento *</label>
              <select id="documentType" name="documentType" required class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]">
                <option value="">Seleccione...</option>
                <option value="DNI">DNI</option>
                <option value="CE">Carnet de Extranjería</option>
                <option value="PAS">Pasaporte</option>
                <option value="RUC">RUC</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Número de Documento *</label>
              <input type="text" id="documentNumber" name="documentNumber" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" />
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Dirección de Domicilio *</label>
              <input type="text" id="address" name="address" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Teléfono / Celular *</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Correo Electrónico *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Sección 2: Identificación del Bien */}
        <section>
          <h3 class="flex items-center text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0d1624] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <span class="bg-[#f04f23] text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] mr-3">2</span>
            Identificación del Bien Contratado
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Tipo *</label>
              <select id="productType" name="productType" required class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]">
                <option value="">Seleccione...</option>
                <option value="Producto">Producto</option>
                <option value="Servicio">Servicio</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Monto Reclamado (S/) *</label>
              <input type="number" step="0.01" id="amount" name="amount" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" placeholder="Ej: 150.00" />
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Descripción del Producto o Servicio *</label>
              <input type="text" id="productDescription" name="productDescription" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px]" placeholder="Ej: Quemador a gas modelo X" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Sección 3: Detalle de la Reclamación */}
        <section>
          <h3 class="flex items-center text-[16px] font-bold text-[#0d1624] mb-6 uppercase tracking-wide">
            <span class="bg-[#f04f23] text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] mr-3">3</span>
            Detalle de la Reclamación y Pedido
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-3">Tipo de Reclamación *</label>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
                <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
                  <input type="radio" name="complaintType" value="Reclamo" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-[#f04f23] bg-slate-50 border-slate-300 focus:ring-[#f04f23]" />
                  <div>
                    <span class="block font-bold text-[#0d1624] text-[14px]">Reclamo</span>
                    <span class="block text-slate-500 text-[12px] mt-0.5">Disconformidad relacionada a los productos o servicios.</span>
                  </div>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
                  <input type="radio" name="complaintType" value="Queja" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-[#f04f23] bg-slate-50 border-slate-300 focus:ring-[#f04f23]" />
                  <div>
                    <span class="block font-bold text-[#0d1624] text-[14px]">Queja</span>
                    <span class="block text-slate-500 text-[12px] mt-0.5">Malestar o descontento respecto a la atención al público.</span>
                  </div>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Detalle de la reclamación *</label>
              <textarea id="complaintDetail" name="complaintDetail" required rows="4" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px] resize-none"></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label class="block text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Pedido del consumidor *</label>
              <textarea id="consumerRequest" name="consumerRequest" required rows="3" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-[#f04f23] text-[14px] resize-none" placeholder="¿Qué solución espera obtener?"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Políticas y Envío */}
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-8 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" required class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-[#f04f23] bg-slate-50 border-slate-300 rounded focus:ring-[#f04f23]" />
            <span class="text-[13px] text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Declaro que los datos consignados son correctos y fieles a la verdad. Asimismo, acepto las <button type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('privacyModal').showModal()" class="text-[#f04f23] underline hover:text-[#d0421c]">Políticas de Privacidad</button> para el tratamiento de mis datos personales en la gestión de esta reclamación.
            </span>
          </label>
          
          <div id="successMessage" class="hidden bg-green-50 text-green-700 p-4 rounded-xl mb-6 text-sm font-medium border border-green-200">
            ✅ Su reclamo ha sido enviado exitosamente. En breve recibirá una copia en su correo electrónico.
          </div>
          
          <div id="errorMessage" class="hidden bg-red-50 text-red-700 p-4 rounded-xl mb-6 text-sm font-medium border border-red-200">
            ❌ Ocurrió un error al enviar el reclamo. Por favor intente nuevamente.
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-end">
            <button id="submitBtn" type="submit" class="bg-[#0d1624] text-white font-bold text-[15px] py-4 px-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-[#1a2538] hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
              <span id="submitText">Enviar Reclamo / Queja</span>
              <svg id="submitIcon" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </form>

      <script>
        const form = document.getElementById('complaintForm') as HTMLFormElement;
        const submitBtn = document.getElementById('submitBtn') as HTMLButtonElement;
        const submitText = document.getElementById('submitText');
        const submitIcon = document.getElementById('submitIcon');
        const successMessage = document.getElementById('successMessage');
        const errorMessage = document.getElementById('errorMessage');

        if (form) {
          form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            
            // UI Loading state
            submitBtn.disabled = true;
            if (submitText) submitText.textContent = 'Enviando...';
            if (submitIcon) submitIcon.classList.add('hidden');
            if (successMessage) successMessage.classList.add('hidden');
            if (errorMessage) errorMessage.classList.add('hidden');

            const formData = new FormData(form);
            const data = Object.fromEntries(formData.entries());

            try {
              const res = await fetch('/api/reclamaciones', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                  'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify(data)
              });

              if (res.ok) {
                if (successMessage) successMessage.classList.remove('hidden');
                form.reset();
              } else {
                if (errorMessage) errorMessage.classList.remove('hidden');
              }
            } catch (error) {
              console.error(error);
              if (errorMessage) errorMessage.classList.remove('hidden');
            } finally {
              // Restore UI
              submitBtn.disabled = false;
              if (submitText) submitText.textContent = 'Enviar Reclamo / Queja';
              if (submitIcon) submitIcon.classList.remove('hidden');
            }
          });
        }
      </script>
    </div>

    {/* Modal de Políticas de Privacidad */}
    <dialog id="privacyModal" class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-0 w-[90%] max-w-2xl backdrop:bg-slate-900/60 backdrop:backdrop-blur-sm fixed top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 m-0 border-0 z-50">
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 max-h-[85vh] overflow-y-auto">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-[#0d1624]">Políticas de Privacidad</h3>
          <button type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('privacyModal').close()" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-[#f04f23] transition-colors focus:outline-none">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="text-[14px] text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>De conformidad con la Ley N° 29733, Ley de Protección de Datos Personales, el usuario otorga su consentimiento expreso para que los datos personales que facilite en este formulario queden incorporados en el Banco de Datos de <strong>GRUPO EMPRESARIAL ZEVALLOS S.A.C.</strong></p>
          <p>Estos datos serán tratados de forma estrictamente confidencial con la finalidad única de gestionar su reclamo o queja, contactarlo para brindarle una respuesta oportuna y llevar un registro estadístico de atención al cliente.</p>
          <p>Usted puede ejercer en cualquier momento sus derechos de acceso, rectificación, cancelación y oposición de sus datos personales comunicándose a nuestro correo electrónico oficial: <strong>privacidad@heatperu.com</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 flex justify-end">
          <button type="button" onclick="document.getElementById('privacyModal').close()" class="bg-[#0d1624] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-[#1a2538] transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-[#0d1624] cursor-pointer">
            Entendido
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dialog>

  </main>
</Layout>
